column1: Baby Barnaby's////Oh my God well I'm not a big breakfast buff usually don't even eat breakfast if I do it's something really small came here this morning a bit hungry but not starving or nothing after looking at the menu for a few minutes sipping on my coffee I asked the waitress what she likes best and she recommended the green egg breakfast they comes with potatoes sausage and toast and an unbelievable this thing was Delicious plate was very big and I cannot believe I finished the whole thing but I did very rare for me this has to be in one of the top 10 breakfast in my life.
